title: Open the door to great living at Links At Forest Creek
posting_body: ['Links At Forest Creek', '20404 Poppy Hills Trl', 'Round Rock, TX 78664', 'A wonderful home in Round Rock is waiting for you!', 'We currently have a gorgeous 2 bedroom 2 bathroom renting for $1649 per month.', 'This unit comes with 958 sq ft.', 'Best Place to Call Home In Round Rock!', "Welcome home to Round Rock's two-bedroom 4-Plex apartment community, The Links at Forest Creek.", 'You will appreciate the controlled access gates and resident oriented focus with monthly planned activities, resort-style pool, and cardio fitness center.', 'show contact info', 'Community Highlights:', '● Business Center', '● Clubhouse', '● Conference Room', '● Controlled Access', '● Online Services', '● On-Site Maintenance', '● Package Service', '● Pet Play Area', '● Picnic Area', '● 24 Hour Emergency Maintenance', '● 24-Hr.', 'Cardio Fitness Center with Free Weights', '● Carport parking at front door included', '● On-Site Property Management & Maintenance', '● Perimeter Fencing with Remote Access Entry', '● Pet-Friendly Community - Large Pets Welcome, No Breed Restrictions', '● Planned Resident Activities', '● Resort Style Pool with Pool Side WiFi', '● Walking/Biking Trails', '● Wireless Community Clubhouse', 'Unit Highlights:', '● Attached Private Covered Parking', '● Black-on-Black Whirlpool Appliances', '● Designer Coordinated Colors', '● Faux Wood Plank Flooring', '● Full-size or Stackable Washer & Dryer Included', '● Nine-Foot & Vaulted Ceilings', '● Patio or Balcony', '● Track Lighting & Ceiling Fans', 'Contact:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>/', 'Leasing Options:', '6-Month, 12-Month', 'Pet Policy:', 'Cats and Dogs Allowed: $15 Monthly Pet Rent.', '$350 Fee for 1 pet, $600 for 2 pets.', '2 Pet Limit.', 'Weight Restrictions Apply.', 'No Breed Restrictions.', 'Management:', 'MEB Management', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', 'F180D1C40845456']
